    public class TimeoutCEPPatternOperator<IN>
extends AbstractCEPPatternOperator<IN,org.apache.flink.types.Either<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<Map<String,IN>,Long>,Map<String,IN>>>
    CEP pattern operator which only returns fully matched event patterns and partially matched event patterns which have timed out wrapped in Either. The matched events are stored in a Map and are indexed by the event names associated in the pattern specification. The fully matched event patterns are returned as a Either.Right instance and the partially matched event patterns are returned as a Either.Left instance.
